{"word":"H1366 - גְּבוּל - gᵉbûwl - gheb-ool' - Border","slug":"H1366","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גְּבוּל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gᵉbûwl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gheb-ool'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Border"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05DC;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05DC; - <a href='S:g'>g</a><sup>e</sup>bu&#x0302;l  gebu&#x0302;l</b> - <i>gheb-ool', gheb-ool'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1379\">H1379</a>; properly a <i>cord</i> (as <i>twisted</i>), that is, (by implication) a <i>boundary</i>; by extension the <i>territory</i> inclosed: - border, bound, coast, X great, landmark, limit, quarter, space."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1367\">H1367</a>, <a href=\"#/H1379\">H1379</a>, <a href=\"#/H1380\">H1380</a>, <a href=\"#/H1381\">H1381</a>, <a href=\"#/H1382\">H1382</a>, <a href=\"#/H1383\">H1383</a>, <a href=\"#/H4020\">H4020</a>"}]}